ISLAMABAD, Mar 11 (APP): Prime Minister Muhammad Shehbaz Sharif on Monday expressed grief over the death of Awami National Party leader Asfandyar Wali Khan’s wife.
Sympathising with the bereaved family, he prayed to Allah Almighty for forgiveness of the departed soul and patience to the family members.
